        "hotelStaticData": {
            "id": "155956",
            "name": "Eurohotel Paris Creteil",
            "description": "Located 7 minutes from the station 'Pointe Du Lac', on the Metro line 8 which serves in a few minutes Grands Boulevards, Bastille, Invalides, Opera and Parc des Expositions. The Hotel Paris Créteil will welcome you in all the modern comforts of a Parisian hotel. All our rooms are air-conditioned, the hotel is also equipped with rooms for people with reduced mobility In addition, our restaurant (120 seats) offers traditional French cuisine accompanied by a fresh buffet honoring our expertise. The hotel Eurohotel Paris Creteil *** is located in the Europarc in Créteil near the A4, A86 (Bercy, Disneyland). To get there by public transport: take metro line 8 and stop at Pointe du Lac station. Our Bar welcomes you 24/24 and 7/7. ",
